6	 *
7	 * Walks corpus/manifest.json, skips private entries, content-hashes
8	 * each file, and (in non-dry-run mode) chunks + embeds + upserts
9	 * into the vector store. Idempotent: re-running with no changes does
10	 * no work, because the per-file content hash is recorded in state.
11	 */
